rComments: Awful professor, Very Poor Lecture. He spent all his time discussing the questions in the textbook. I'd rather study by myself, and watch study videos on YouTube. For exams, even if you just have a small mistake, you will lose the whole marks for that question. Just Avoid him if you can.

The most common lines he said was "Who agrees this? Who disagrees this?" I think he doesn't know how to teach, instead buying time like this. He spent 1 hour to explain 2 lines in the text book which was already explained in the book. WHAT A WONDERFUL LECTURE!
